-(LOUD CLANG)
-(GLASS SHATTERS)

00:28.125 --> 00:29.125
Huh?

00:30.666 --> 00:32.083
(CLANGING CONTINUES)

00:39.625 --> 00:40.708
(BEEPS)

00:45.666 --> 00:46.666
(GASPS)

00:48.500 --> 00:50.333
(WATER DRIPPING)

00:57.500 --> 00:58.500
I am Groot.

01:00.458 --> 01:01.500
I am Groot.

01:03.291 --> 01:04.375
Hmm.

01:06.250 --> 01:09.083
-(PLEASANT MUSIC PLAYING)
-Hmm. Hmm.

01:09.958 --> 01:11.375
(TOILET FLUSHING)

01:19.083 --> 01:20.291
Hmm...

01:23.625 --> 01:24.708
(GASPS)

01:26.583 --> 01:28.500
-(RATTLING)
-I am Groot.

01:29.250 --> 01:30.541
I am Groot.

01:32.250 --> 01:33.458
I am Groot.

01:37.208 --> 01:38.208
(GASPS)

01:40.750 --> 01:41.833
(GRUNTS)

01:47.666 --> 01:49.333
AUTOMATED VOICE 1:
<i>You have walked 300 steps--</i>

01:49.416 --> 01:50.875
AUTOMATED VOICE 2:
<i>To know your horse--</i>

01:50.958 --> 01:52.833
AUTOMATED VOICE 3:
<i>Didn't find any work out history--</i>

01:52.916 --> 01:54.875
-(EXPLOSION)
-(GASPS)

02:08.708 --> 02:10.708
(EERIE MUSIC PLAYING)

02:14.791 --> 02:16.125
I am Groot.

02:19.541 --> 02:21.291
-I am Groot.
-I am Groot.

02:21.375 --> 02:22.458
(GASPS)

02:22.541 --> 02:23.666
(GROWLS)

02:27.333 --> 02:29.333
(UPBEAT SALSA MUSIC PLAYING)

02:48.000 --> 02:49.666
Oh, no, no, my friend. Try again.

02:49.750 --> 02:52.041
It's not step, step, turn.
It's step, step, pirouette.

02:52.125 --> 02:54.208
Now, you spin like this...
Into a large angular shape.

02:53.708 --> 02:56.750
quite big, strike a pose and then bring
your body back in. Breathe in and out.

02:57.416 --> 02:59.041
Three times. One, two, three.

02:59.125 --> 03:01.125
See, when you dance,
watch my feet closely like this.

03:01.208 --> 03:03.250
And a one, and two. It's all in the hips.

03:03.333 --> 03:05.333
Look at me. Four, five, six.
Cha, cha, cha.

03:05.416 --> 03:07.416
And now, I have a few points of criticism

03:07.500 --> 03:09.333
that I think could improve your dancing.

03:09.416 --> 03:10.833
GROOT: Mm-hmm.

03:11.666 --> 03:12.666
Mm-hmm.

03:12.750 --> 03:14.166
(SCREAMING)

03:14.916 --> 03:16.083
I am Groot.

03:17.000 --> 03:18.833
(SALSA MUSIC CONTINUES)
